<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WorkWise - Home</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/homepage.css">
    <style>
        /* Fix header consistency */
        #header-placeholder {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            background-color: white;
        }
        
        /* Ensure footer stays at bottom */
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .container {
            flex: 1;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Include the header -->
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <section class="hero">
        <div id="jobCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="https://img.freepik.com/premium-photo/avenue-katsura-trees-full-bloom-autumn-people_1106493-64659.jpg?w=1380"
                        class="d-block w-100" alt="Office Work">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h3>Find Your Dream Job</h3>
                        <p>Explore thousands of job opportunities in various industries.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1310441327/photo/microsoft-france-headquarters-entrance-in-issy-les-moulineaux-near-paris.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=w4df4OwilAGtPb01aXv910ND85E9Vh0I8qZ4CuRbFqI="
                        class="d-block w-100" alt="Corporate Career">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h3>Top Companies Hiring</h3>
                        <p>Connect with leading companies worldwide.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="https://kadence.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Amazon-HQ-in-Sunnyvale-California.jpg"
                        class="d-block w-100" alt="Startup Team">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h3>Build Your Future</h3>
                        <p>Take your career to the next level with exciting job offers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#jobCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#jobCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h2 class="text-center">About WorkWise</h2>
        <p class="text-center">WorkWise is your trusted job search partner, connecting job seekers with top employers. Whether you're looking for full-time, part-time, or remote jobs, we have opportunities waiting for you.</p>
    </div>


    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h2 class="text-center">What Our Users Say</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-3">
                    <p>"WorkWise helped me find my dream job within weeks. The platform is user-friendly and the job listings are up-to-date."</p>
                    <p class="text-end"><strong>- Sarah Johnson</strong></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-3">
                    <p>"As a recruiter, I've found excellent candidates through WorkWise. The quality of applicants is consistently high."</p>
                    <p class="text-end"><strong>- Michael Chen</strong></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-3">
                    <p>"The career resources on WorkWise are invaluable. I improved my resume and interview skills significantly."</p>
                    <p class="text-end"><strong>- Emily Rodriguez</strong></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Include the footer -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="assets/auth.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/homepage.js"></script>
</body>

</html> 